## Quick start

```csharp
using WoW.Two.Sdk.Backend.Beta.{AreaPath};

var builder = WebApplication.CreateBuilder(args);

// Default registration
builder.Services.AddWowTwo{ModuleName}();

// Or with options
builder.Services.AddWowTwo{ModuleName}(opts =>
{
    opts.Example = "custom";
});

// Or from config (binds section "{ModuleName}" by default)
builder.Services.AddWowTwo{ModuleName}(builder.Configuration);

var app = builder.Build();
app.Run();
```

